result:
<v-card
  hover
  width="200px"
  :to="`/users/${user.id}`"
>
  <v-img
    :src="userImage"
    height="256px"
  >
  </v-img>

  <v-card-actions>
    <v-icon>person</v-icon>
    <v-card-title v-text="user.name"></v-card-title>
  </v-card-actions>

  <v-card-actions>
    <v-icon>email</v-icon>
    <v-card-title v-text="user.email"></v-card-title>
  </v-card-actions>
  
  <v-card-actions>
    <v-icon>people</v-icon>
    <v-card-title v-if="user.team" v-text="user.team.name"></v-card-title>
  </v-card-actions>
</v-card>
